<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> This interpretation of the argument is based on the reviews by <a href="/wiki/Dan_Dennett" title="Dan Dennett" class="mw-redirect">Dan Dennett</a> and <a href="/wiki/PZ_Myers" title="PZ Myers">PZ Myers</a>.</li>
