<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> also (Wilson 2007 <a href="http://www.skeptic.com/eskeptic/07-07-04.html#feature" class="external free" title="http://www.skeptic.com/eskeptic/07-07-04.html#feature" rel="nofollow">http://www.skeptic.com/eskeptic/07-07-04.html#feature</a>). This latter kind of criticism, Dawkins has called "I'm an atheist buttery". <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFDawkins">Dawkins, Richard. <a href="http://richarddawkins.net/article,318,Im-an-atheist-BUT---,Richard-Dawkins" class="external text" title="http://richarddawkins.net/article,318,Im-an-atheist-BUT---,Richard-Dawkins" rel="nofollow">"I'm an atheist, BUT..."</a>. <i>RichardDawkins.net</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://richarddawkins.net/article,318,Im-an-atheist-BUT---,Richard-Dawkins" class="external free" title="http://richarddawkins.net/article,318,Im-an-atheist-BUT---,Richard-Dawkins" rel="nofollow">http://richarddawkins.net/article,318,Im-an-atheist-BUT---,Richard-Dawkins</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-09-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=I%27m+an+atheist%2C+BUT...&amp;rft.atitle=RichardDawkins.net&amp;rft.aulast=Dawkins&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft.au=Dawkins%2C+Richard&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fricharddawkins.net%2Farticle%2C318%2CIm-an-atheist-BUT---%2CRichard-Dawkins&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_God_Delusion"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
