<li><a href="http://richarddawkins.net/article,303,Reading-of-The-God-Delusion-in-Lynchburg-VA,Richard-Dawkins--C-SPAN2" class="external text" title="http://richarddawkins.net/article,303,Reading-of-The-God-Delusion-in-Lynchburg-VA,Richard-Dawkins--C-SPAN2" rel="nofollow">Video: Dawkins' reading from <i>The God Delusion</i> at Randolph-Macon Woman's College</a> – including the Question-and-Answer afterwards. Oct. 23, 2006</li>
